Texts.Eng: A Hylotl, eh?

Texts.Chs: 一只猴子！哦等等，猴子是有尾巴的。它是一只猿！
Texts.Eng: A monkey! Oh wait, monkeys have tails. An ape!

Texts.Chs: 一只会说话的猴子。真酷。
Texts.Eng: A talking monkey. Cool.
Aaaaghhhh!!

Texts.Chs: Aiee!!!额，对不起--我对猩猩有一种天然的恐惧，而你的脸...额...不好意思...
Texts.Eng: Aah!!! Oh, sorry - I have an irrational fear of chimpanzees, and your face... er... Sorry...
Ace meeting you.
Alright mate?
Alright, I get the message.  I'm gone.
Alright?

Texts.Chs: 我遇到的另一个叶族人告诉了我关于天界塔的事情。真吓人。
Texts.Eng: Another Avian I met told me about the Celestial Towers. Chilling.

Texts.Chs: 今天发生了什么有趣的事情了吗？
Texts.Eng: Anything interesting happening today?

Texts.Chs: 所有的猿族人都擅长科技？很不巧它是我在学校里最差的科目。
Texts.Eng: Are all Apex good at science? It was my worst subject at school.

Texts.Chs: 猿族人仍在迁徙吗？你什么时候得到这些尾巴的？
Texts.Eng: Are the Apex continuously devolving? When do you get tails?
Are you gonna hurt me?

Texts.Chs: 你是由纯能量构成的吗？
Texts.Eng: Are you made of pure energy?
Avians are SO COOL!

Texts.Chs: 遇见你真是棒极了，猿族人！
Texts.Eng: Awesome to see you, Apex!

Texts.Chs: 变成一只史莱姆确实让我对这些小东西的看法发生了很大的变化。
Texts.Eng: Becoming a slime really changed my opinion of those little slimes.

Texts.Chs: 我能借根羽毛做羽毛笔吗？
Texts.Eng: Can I borrow a feather to make a quill?
Can you go in the water?

Texts.Chs: 你能让这些事情重回正轨吗？
Texts.Eng: Can you put things back the way they were?
Can you read?

Texts.Chs: 你就不能把这些事情恢复正常吗?
Texts.Eng: Can't you just fix things back to normal?

Texts.Chs: 你能不能只扫描、复制这些或者其他东西，而不是拿走它？
Texts.Eng: Can't you just scan and replicate that or something instead of taking it?
Come on, <entityname>.  I can't live like this.

Texts.Chs: 你能在战斗中击败鲨鱼吗？也许这就像在问我自己能不能在战斗中击败老虎一样。
Texts.Eng: Could you beat a shark in a fight? Maybe that's like asking if I could beat a tiger in a fight.

Texts.Chs: 你能替我补上那个洞吗？
Texts.Eng: Could you patch that hole for me?

Texts.Chs: 你能抽个时间教我打猎吗？
Texts.Eng: Could you teach me how to hunt some time?

Texts.Chs: 你有听说过我们的星球Glitch吗？我们现在该怎么办？
Texts.Eng: Did you hear about our planet, Glitch? What do we do now?
Did you need me?

Texts.Chs: 猿族看起来是不是有点像曾经的我们？额，嗯...我的意思是，像人类？
Texts.Eng: Didn't the Apex look kind of like us once?  Oh, uh... I mean like humans?

Texts.Chs: 叶族有被巨大的蜂鸟袭击过吗？
Texts.Eng: Do Floran ever get attacked by giant hummingbirds?

Texts.Chs: 叶族是不是曾长到250英尺高，像长着张脸的红杉树一样？
Texts.Eng: Do Floran ever get like 250ft tall, like a sequoia tree with a face?
Do Hylotl ever dry out?

Texts.Chs: 你有没有更换过你的眼球？
Texts.Eng: Do you ever have to replace your eye bulbs?

Texts.Chs: 你只能一直发光，还是能像开关一样随心所欲控制？
Texts.Eng: Do you glow all the time, or is it like a switch you can turn off?

Texts.Chs: 你们这些家伙有花粉吗？
Texts.Eng: Do you guys have pollen?

Texts.Chs: 你有眼睛吗？你是怎么看得见的？
Texts.Eng: Do you have eyes? How do you even see?

Texts.Chs: 你发出的光在晚上会吸引虫子吗？我收集虫子...
Texts.Eng: Does your glow attract bugs at night? I collect bugs...

Texts.Chs: 不要想这些东西。我们的身体有毒。
Texts.Eng: Don't even think about it.  Our bodies are toxic.

Texts.Chs: 不要担心，触摸我们不会腐蚀你的手指或其他部位。
Texts.Eng: Don't worry, touching us won't corrode your fingers or anything.

Texts.Chs: 别担心，我们不是黏糊糊的生物。你的羽毛是安全的。
Texts.Eng: Don't worry, we're not too sticky.  Your feathers are safe.

Texts.Chs: 每次我看到一个正常人，我都有点担心他们可能是粗鲁的人。
Texts.Eng: Every time I see a regular human, I get a little worried that they might be rude.
Florans are the best!
Geez...
Go go go!
Good to see you.
Great to see you, pal.
Guards!!
Hah, oh my, you smell funny.
Hah, we're both slimy!

Texts.Chs: 你有听说过'怪物麝香'吗？
Texts.Eng: Have you ever heard of 'Monster Musume'?

Texts.Chs: 作为人类，你有尝试过剃胡子吗？
Texts.Eng: Have you ever tried shaving to pass as human?

Texts.Chs: 吃过瓜子吗？我想你会喜欢上它们的。
Texts.Eng: Have you ever tried sunflower seeds? I think you'd love them.

Texts.Chs: 嗨！额，我希望那没有冒犯到你。
Texts.Eng: Hello! Uh, I hope that wasn't offensive.
Hello, fellow slime.
Hello.
Hellooo.
Help!
Here you go, <entityname>.

Texts.Chs: 过来，我想让你拿着这个。
Texts.Eng: Here, I'd like you to have this.
Hey there, Apex!
Hey there, Avian!
Hey! Welcome!
Hey, <entityname>.  Did you need anything?
Hey, ape-dude!
Hey, great to see you.
Hey, it's a big bird!
Hey, nice to meet you.
Hey, what're you doing?
Hey, what's happening?
Hey, what's up?
Hey, you jelly?  So am I!  Ha!
How do you work?
How're things?
How's it going?
How's it?
How's life treating you?
Howdy.

Texts.Chs: 鲛族艺术真不错，我是粉丝之一。
Texts.Eng: Hylotl art is pretty nice, I'm a fan.
I bet you're popular at parties!
I bet you've killed more monsters than I've had hot dinners.
I don't read a lot of poetry, I find it too opaque.
I don't think I've been sick even once since I mutated.
I don't wanna die!
I draw a little, maybe you'd like to take a look sometime?
I got my eye on you, Floran.
I had a pizza with tuna and bananas on it once. Surprisingly good.
I hear you and the fish people don't get on?
I hear your architecture is stunning.
I hear your kind build grand temples. We used to do that too.
I hope that doesn't happen too often.
I hope this'll do.
I hope your future tenants are treated better than this.
I like being squishy.
I like birds; my uncle used to own parrots.
I liked this place the way it was before.
I love the way you guys talk.
I met a greenfinger once - real nice guy... Or girl... Or neither?
I miss the cool sea breeze.
I once made a Glitch costume out of cardboard.
I saw one of those Avian towers once. People jump off those!?
I still live here.  Why'd you put up another deed?
I study intergalactic religions - Kluex is just fascinating.
I think I'll pass on going for a swim.
I too am flightless.
I used to be expedition's xenobiologist, but I didn't want to hurt the slimes.
I used to live by a beach on Earth. I miss it.
I used to meditate, but I couldn't stand the quiet.
I used to work in a robotics lab.
I want armour like yours.
I want to go into spear production, do you think there's a market for it?
I was in the slime world when I heard what happened to Earth.
I wish I was a Floran.
I'd help, but I don't have a weapon!  Can you help them?!
I'm feeling a bit of a draft here.
I'm in a hurry, gotta fly. Oops, sorry, that was insensitive.
I'm scared of you.
I've always wanted to hang out with a robot.
I've had some problems with water ever since I became a slimeperson, but I'm still a pretty good swimmer.
I've heard Floran can be pretty vicious, but you seem kinda nice.
I've heard bad things about the Miniknog, I'm not surprised you joined the Protectorate.
I've never met a Miniknog soldier. Are they scary?
I've never met an Avian I didn't like.
I've read ten books!
I've read that most of your kind are savages. You don't seem to be.
If an Avian and a snake had a baby, would it be a feather boa?
If anyone's got a weapon, take that thing out!!
If things stay in this state, I'm heading elsewhere.
It'd have been nice to be informed beforehand about this sorta thing.
It's hard to believe Floran could be lethal killers.
It's kinda nice living out here.  Much more peaceful.
It's pretty exciting to see you!
It's weird that you can't fly.
Just how big IS Big Ape?
KILL IT!!  KILL IT!!
Living under water is cool.
My dad is a mechanic, but I guess in Glitch terms he's a doctor.
Nice face.
Nice feathers there.
Nice meeting ya!
Nice outfit, where'd you get it?
Nice to meet you!
Nice to meet you, fishface.
No bones about it, robots are just awesome.
Oh come on, stop it!
Oh geez, somebody help!
Oh geez, uh... hello.
Oh hey!
Oh hey, a giant fish.
Oh hey, how's it going?
Oh shoot, HELP!!
Oh wow, I've never seen anyone like you before!
Oh wow, you're made of plasma.
Okay, I've never seen anyone like you before.
Our planet had many oceans. Then a tentacle monster happened.
Ow, my eyes. You're super bright.
Please, help them!!
Pleasure to make your acquaintance, ape.
Put that back, please.
Safe!  For the moment.
Seals are like dogs, but in the sea. All Hylotl should have seals.
So lovely to meet you, Glitch!
Some people tried eating slime jelly once.  Their bodies melted from the inside out.
Somebody do something!
Something about you makes me want fish and chips. Can't put my finger on what.
Something doesn't feel right.
Sometimes I like to pretend I'm an old timey knight!
Sorry that the Apex are all oppressed and stuff.
Stop stealing my stuff!
Suddenly remembering working in my old xenobiology lab...
Survived another day.  Whew...
Take 'em out!
Talking fish, sharks with legs... man, I love space!
Thank you!
Thanks for dropping by!
That's a nice alloy you've got there.
That's a pretty cool glow you've got going there.
That's it I'm outta here.
The Glitch have a funny way of talking... Cuts out the flim-flam though.
The Hylotl strive for peace, right? Same as humans. No wonder you're a Protector.
The Miniknog sounds terrible!
This place could use a better defense setup.
This place's already occupied.
This place's seen better days.
Those poor monkeys... ... what?  Oh, uh... nothing!
Time to set up shop somewhere else, I guess.
We decided to leave the other slimes in peace after all that happened.
We should hang out more often, fish.
Welcome!
Welcome, Hylotl!
Well, you're something I've not seen before.
What are you? ...Whatever you are, I like it.
What metal are you made from?
What you up to?
What're you doing, <entityname>?
What's going on here?
What's it like to be made of metal?
What's up, <entityname>?
What's up?
When I was a child I had a toy monkey that looked like you.
Where the heck's a guard when you need one?!
Where's a toolbox when you need one?!
Which meat is the best meat?
Who created you guys, then?
Who is "Big Ape"?
Who's this Kluex I keep hearing about, then?
Whoa, you're something new alright...
Whoo!
Why didn't I take a weapon with me?!
Wow, you're pretty brightly coloured! Are you off to a festival?
Yo there, Floran.
Yo!
You Novakids are awesome.
You alright?
You could do with a pruning.
You good?
You guys are so cool.
You have the coolest face.
You look pretty strong, like a wrestler.
You look so cool. I wish I was you.
You look so warm and fluffy.
You make me think of the garden I had when I was growing up on Earth.
You reek of wet dog! Or, I guess, wet ape.
You remind me of holidays at the beach.
You seem like a cultured kind of person.
You seem like a nice sort.
You would be a terrible "murder in the dark" player.
You're a bit creaky, maybe you should oil your joints.
You're not from around here, are you?
You're one slick fish man.
You're pretty awesome for a talking tuna.
You're pretty cute.
You're quite small for a killer robot.
You're so bright!
You're so pretty.
Your hair is just magnificent.
